{"title_page": "Teen Mom UK", "text_new": "{{primary sources|date=May 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2018}}\n{{Use British English|date=March 2018}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Teen Mom UK\n| image              = \n| genre              = [[Reality Television]] \n| language           = English\n| country            = United Kingdom\n| num_series         = 6\n| num_episodes       = 40\n| company    = [[True North Productions]]\n| network            = [[MTV (UK and Ireland)|MTV International]]\n| picture_format     = [[16:9]] [[1080i]] [[High-definition television|HDTV]]\n| audio_format        = [[Stereophonic sound|Stereo]]\n| first_aired        = {{Start date|2016|11|02|df=y}}\n| last_aired         = present\n| related            = ''[[Teen Mom]]''\n| website            = http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk\n}}\n\n'''''Teen Mom UK''''' is a British reality television series set in the United Kingdom. It is a spin-off of the American franchise ''[[Teen Mom]]''. It currently airs on [[MTV (UK and Ireland)|MTV]]. The series was first announced in September 2016.<ref name=\"Article2\">{{cite news |title=Teen Mom UK: Start date confirmed for brand new MTV series! |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uk-start-date-confirmed-for-smash-hit-mtv-format}}</ref> It follows the lives of five British teenage mums who are trying to make it through motherhood. In July 2017, the series showed in the U.S. under the name '''''Teen Mum'''''.\n\n== Series overview ==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"|Series\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Episodes\n!colspan=\"2\"|Originally aired\n|-\n! First aired\n! Last aired\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FF5F5F;\"|\n| [[#Series 1 (2016)|1]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2016|11|2|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2016|12|21|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#0050C8;\"|\n| [[#Series 2 (2017)|2]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2017|7|26|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2017|9|13|df=y}}\n