end Jordan Edwards. Chloe & Jordan admit that they didn't plan on starting a family so young. Throughout the seasons of Teen Mom UK, we see Chloe dealing with baby blues, as well as maintaining relationships with friends and family.<ref name=\"Article1\"/>\n\n=== Megan Salmon Ferrari ===\n'''Megan Salmon-Ferrari''' (from [[Chelmsford]], [[Essex]])\n\nMegan had her son Mckenzie with her first boyfriend, Dylan Siggers, when she was 17 years old .<ref name=\"Article1\"/> They lived in a caravan on Dylan's Mum and Dad's drive.\n\nIn mid-2016, a few weeks after Mckenzie was born, Dylan proposed to Megan,<ref name=\"Article3\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk extended preview: megan salmon ferrari and dylan siggers get engaged: 'i was so shocked' |url=https://instagram.com/p/BLqSwaTAKdJ/}}</ref> however the engagement was short-lived, with Megan discovering that Dylan had been unfaithful.<ref name=\"Article5\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk airs and fans have their say on megan salmon ferrari's fianc\u00e9 dylan siggers cheating on her with her bff |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uk-airs-and-fans-have-their-say-on-megan-salmon-ferrari-and-dylan-siggers-dramz}}</ref> The couple later reconciled, with Dylan proposing to Megan once again while they were on holiday together in [[Spain]].<ref name=\"Article7\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk spoiler video: dylan proposes to megan again as the two enjoy quality time together on holiday |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uk-spoiler-video-aww-dylan-proposes-to-megan-again-during-birthday-holiday}}</ref>\n\nMegan announced that her & Dylan were expecting their second child in November 2016,<ref name=\"Insta1\">{{cite web |title=Megan Salmon-Ferrari Instagram |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BNG-BJcB-j_/}}</ref> their daughter, Dulcie Mae, was born in March 2017.<ref name=\"Article8\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk's megan salmon-ferrari announces birth of her second child |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uks-megan-salmonferrari-announces-birth-of-her-second-child}}</ref><ref name=\"Insta2\">{{cite web |title=Megan Salmon-Ferrari Instagram |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BSPEfPpg3uj/}}</ref>\n\nMegan took a break from series 4, to focus on herself, children and other projects. Megan returned to Teen Mom UK for series 5.\n\n=== Mia Boardman ===\n'''Mia Boardman''' (from [[Southampton]], [[Hampshire]])\n\nMia was 9 months pregnant with Marliya when she started filming Teen Mom UK at the age of 19.<ref name=\"Article1\"/> The birth of Marliya was captured for the show, with Mia's plans for a natural birth being derailed after the baby's heartbeat dropped, forcing her to have a [[cesarian section]].<ref name=\"Article6\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk sneak peek: mia gives birth to daughter marliya - but her natural birth doesn't go to plan |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uk-spoiler-mia-gives-birth-to-daughter-marliya-but-her-natural-birth-doesnt-go-to-plan}}</ref>\n\nMarliya's father is Mia's ex-boyfriend Manley Geddes, they were teenage sweethearts. The couple separated for a few years before filming and during that time Manley had Aalayah with ex Erin,<ref name=\"Article4\">{{cite news |title=teen mom uk girls appear on this morning as mia boardman admits she's 'always jealous' of boyfriend manley's relationship with his ex |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/teen-mom-uk/news/teen-mom-uk-girls-on-this-morning-mia-boardman-admits-shes-always-jealous-of-boyfriend-manleys-relationship-with-his-ex}}</ref> with whom he briefly reunited. The relationship has since ended. Throughout the series of Teen Mom UK, we saw Mia struggle with the relationship between boyfriend Manley & Erin.\n\nMia left after series 3 to focus more on her new relationship and her career.\nMia appeared as a guest in Chloe's segment in series 5.\n\n=== Naomi Konickova ===\n'''Naomi Konickova''' (from [[London]])\n \nNaomi had daughter Kyanna at the age of 17, with boyfriend Raphael Poitou.<ref name=\"Article1\"/> The show followed Naomi whilst training to be a makeup artist and she says that becoming a mum has made her aspire to achieve her dream even more, as well as covering the rocky relationship between Naomi & Kyanna's father. She has now quit teen mom to pursue her singing career in the USA. She has sold out many famous venues such as Madison Square Garden touring all over America.\n\n=== Sassi Simmonds ===\n'''Sassi Simmonds''' (from [[Stockport]])\n \nSassi has daughter Zena'ya Saint. She has been with boyfriend Darren since school and are childhood sweethearts. Sassi joined the cast of Teen Mom UK at the start of season 2, after the departure of Naomi Konickova.\n\n=== Shannon Wise ===\n'''Shannon Wise''' (from [[High Wycombe]], [[Buckinghamshire]])\n\nShannon has son Theodore with on/off boyfriend Charlie. She joined the cast of Teen Mom UK at the start of season 4, after the departure of Mia Boardman. During series 5 it was revealed that Shannon was pregnant with her and Charlie's second child, due July 2019.However,Shannon has decided to take a break in season 7 to focus on family.\n\n== Timeline of cast members ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" width=\"70%\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\u201d style=\"width:5%;\" | Name\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"6\"  | Series\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 1\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 2\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 3\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 4\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 5\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:7%;\" | 6\n\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Amber Butler\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Chloe Patton\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Megan Salmon-Ferrari\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{N/A|}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Mia Boardman\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{N/A|}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{cGuest}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| s