 to make it through motherhood. In July 2017, the series showed in the U.S. under the name '''''Teen Mum'''''.\n\n== Series overview ==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"|Series\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Episodes\n!colspan=\"2\"|Originally aired\n|-\n! First aired\n! Last aired\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FF5F5F;\"|\n| [[#Series 1 (2016)|1]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2016|11|2|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2016|12|21|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#0050C8;\"|\n| [[#Series 2 (2017)|2]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2017|7|26|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2017|9|13|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#00AE00;\"|\n| [[#Series 3 (2018)|3]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2018|3|14|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2018|5|2|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFF00;\"|\n| [[#Series 4 (2018)|4]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2018|9|5|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2018|10|24|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FF69B4;\" |\n| [[#Series 5 (2019)|5]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2019|1|23|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2019|3|13|df=y}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#22CC88;\"|\n| [[#Series 6 (2019)|6]]\n| 8\n| {{Start date|2019|7|24|df=y}}\n| {{End date|2019|9|11|df=y}}\n|}\n\n== Episodes ==\n=== Series 1 (2016) ===\n{{Episode table |background=#FF5F5F |overall=5 |season=5 |title=30 |airdate=25 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 1\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n |Title           = Episode 1\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2016|11|2}}\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = FF5F5F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 2\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n |Title           = Episode 2\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2016|11|9}}\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = FF5F5F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 3\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n |Title           = Episode 3\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2016|11|16}}\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = FF5F5F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 4\n |